(17,NULL,'page_detail','Financial Aid','<p>In driving and transforming JGU towards excellence, financial assistance has been provided to outstanding and deserving students to acquire quality education. The funds are distributed through various means including collaborative efforts between JGU and several public and private institutional partners. All scholarships, sponsorship and financial aid are offered through the Yayasan MSU Global&nbsp;and the following scheme:<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n<strong>Beasiswa KIP Kuliah Merdeka</strong><br />\r\nOne of the annual scholarships at JGU, a collaboration between the government and universities to provide full opportunities to prospective students who want to study with full funding and receive pocket money. Indonesia continues to be committed to focusing on improving human resource development through various smart efforts. The Indonesian Smart College Card (KIP-Kuliah) is one of the efforts to help the hopes of students who have economic limitations but excel to continue their studies in higher education.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Beasiswa Foster Parent</strong><br />\r\nIn order to realize one of the national goals, namely the intellectual life of the nation, continuous improvement of the quality of education. The Jakarta Global University Foster Parents Scholarship Program is here as a solution that supports the state to help students who are economically disadvantaged but have a high enthusiasm to learn and achieve their goals by continuing to higher education levels. In collaboration with Foster Parents, Jakarta Global University will provide financial aid subsidies for the education of underprivileged students. This scholarship program involves the financial participation of people who are able to help with tuition fees for students to study at Jakarta Global University, of course with high motivation to become superior human resources and ready to face the industry in the future.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Including several partial scholarships available at JGU, including:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Transforming Lives Scholarship</li>\r\n	<li>Enriching Future Scholarship</li>\r\n	<li>Industry CSR Scholarship</li>\r\n	<li>Academic Scholarship</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n','financial-aid',NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'','','','','2023-11-08 16:10:31',NULL,NULL,NULL,1),
