(39,NULL,'page_detail','Faculty of Information Sciences and Engineering','<p><em><strong>Jakarta Global University offers 7 study programs in the field of information and engineering programs inculding: Bachelor and Master.</strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Faculty of Information Sciences &amp; Engineering (FISE) at Jakarta Global University (JGU) comprises the two departments of Engineering &amp; Technology, and Information Sciences &amp; Computing. Specialization is early and plenty, with close to 6 programmes offered. FISE aims to produce technically competent and well-rounded professionals. Its curricula integrate knowledge of new technological marvels with diverse human values and global perspectives. Soft skills supplement core knowledge and technical skills, resulting in capable graduates enriched by their holistic learning experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a href=\"http://jgu.ac.id/fise/industrial-engineering\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Bachelor in Industrial Engineering</span></span></span></a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"http://jgu.ac.id/fise/informatics-engineering\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Bachelor in Informatics Engineering</span></span></span></a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"http://jgu.ac.id/fise/mechanical-engineering\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Bachelor in Mechanical Engineering</span></span></span></a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"http://jgu.ac.id/fise/civil-engineering\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Bachelor in Civil Engineering</span></span></span></a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"http://jgu.ac.id/fise/electrical-engineering\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Bachelor in Electrical Engineering</span></span></span></a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"http://jgu.ac.id/fise/master-electrical-engineering\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Masters in Electrical Engineering</span></span></span></a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n','Faculty-of-Information-Sciences-and-Engineering',NULL,NULL,'fise-jgu-banner_20210120164530.jpg',NULL,'','','','','2023-11-08 16:10:31',NULL,NULL,NULL,1),
