(117,NULL,'news_detail','The Blessing of Iftar with Alumni & Student Organization','<p>Depok (24/05/2021) - The Blessing of Iftar with Alumni &amp; Student Organization has been held at the Main Campus of Jakarta Global University. The event took place lively with several series of events starting from a warm welcome by the JGU Rector, Prof. Dr. apt. Eddy Yusuf, M.Pharm and Chief Executive of the event Onki Alenxander, BCM., M.IT., followed by entertainment performances by JGU Acoustic (collaboration of lecturers and students)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>All participants are required to wear a mask during the event process.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In this activity, the event was attended by JGU Alumni, MSU Indonesia Alumni, Ormawa, Lecturers &amp; Employees of Jakarta Global University. At the core session, there were Tazqiroh and Prayer, introduction to JAGUAS (alumni), Ormawa, and remarks by MSU Indonesia Alumni, followed by the delivery of JGU&#39;s flagship program on the Foster Parent Scholarship Program.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This activity starts at 15.30 WIB - 18.30 WIB, which is closed with maghrib prayer together at the JICC (JGU Islamic Cultural Center) and continues to eat together.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hopefully this event will be able to connect all elements, to continue to work together and collaborate in order to achieve JGU&#39;s vision in the future.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>#BlessingRamadan #JGUIftar #OpenBersama #AyoKeJGU #Bukber</p>\r\n\r\n<blockquote class=\"instagram-media\" data-instgrm-permalink=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/COHf8wih0Ba/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading\" data-instgrm-version=\"13\" style=\" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:540px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);\"><div style=\"padding:16px;\"> <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/COHf8wih0Ba/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading\" style