(143,NULL,'news_detail','Global Partner Program, Visit From MSU Malaysia Student','<p>Pleased to Meet School of Hospitality &amp; Creative Arts, MSU Malaysia Students at JGU Campus: Striving for Success as Balanced, Holistic, and Well-Rounded Individuals</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Jakarta, 31 June 2022&nbsp;- It is with great pleasure that we announce the successful meeting between the students from the renowned School of Hospitality &amp; Creative Arts, MSU Malaysia, and the esteemed faculty at JGU Campus. The encounter, marked by a shared commitment to excellence, witnessed a profound exchange of ideas, fostering a positive atmosphere of growth and development.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>During the interaction, it was evident that the students from MSU Malaysia not only displayed exceptional academic prowess but also showcased remarkable soft skills. Their ability to communicate effectively, collaborate seamlessly, and engage in critical thinking reflected their holistic approach to education and their aspiration to become well-rounded individuals.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The students&#39; exemplary dedication and drive serve as a testament to their unwavering pursuit of success. Their commitment to achieving a harmonious balance between academic and personal growth positions them as potential future leaders in their respective fields.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As the students embark on their journey to Indonesia, we extend our warmest wishes for an enriching and transformative experience. Indonesia&#39;s captivating culture, awe-inspiring landscapes, and warm hospitality are sure to offer a plethora of opportunities for exploration and personal development.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We encourage the students to embrace the diverse Indonesian culture, immerse themselves in novel experiences, and forge enduring connections. May their voyage be filled with joy, enlightenment, and unforgettable memories, further propelling their personal and professional growth.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Jakarta Global University,<br />\r\nManagement and Science University, Malaysia.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/MSUMalaysia/\" tabindex=\"0\">@MSUMalaysia</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/explore/tags/gmp/\" tabindex=\"0\">#GMP</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/explore/tags/jgumsu/\" tabindex=\"0\">#JGUMSU</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/explore/tags/globalpartner/\" tabindex=\"0\">#GlobalPartner</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/explore/tags/mitrakerjasama/\" tabindex=\"0\">#MitraKerjasama</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/explore/tags/ayokejgu/\" tabindex=\"0\">#AyoKeJGU</a></p>\r\n\r\n<blockquote class=\"instagram-media\" data-instgrm-permalink=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CflMAs7P17B/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading\" data-instgrm-version=\"14\" style=\" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:540px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);\"><div style=\"padding:16px;\"> <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CflMAs7P17B/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading\" style=\" background:#FFFFFF; line-height:0; padding:0 0; text-align:center; text-decoration:none; width:100%;\" target=\"_blank\"> <div style=\" display: flex; flex-direction: row; align-items: center;\"> <div style=\"background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;\"></div> <div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;\"> <div style=\" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;\"></div> <div style=\" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;\"></div></div></div><div style=\"padding: 19% 0;\"></div> <div style=\"display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;\"><svg width=\"50px\" h